{"tid":2341690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【fc】土耳其剛公布科興疫苗有效率為是fake news","createTime":"2020-12-26T14:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T16:03:01.000Z","uid":261647,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"82f1f6956ab0301b99cca0cbb4b7d4d47d2dfb4f","tid":2341690,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:35:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/3823180304388341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fposts%2F3823180304388341&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUiLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=5d193693\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/3823180304388341</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：前線科技人員<br />\n <br />\n問：土耳其剛公布科興疫苗有效率為 91.25%，這數字是否可信？<br />\n<br />\n答：否。因為此乃非正式數據。土耳其的第三階段測試包括 7371 名志願者，但有效率數字只包括當中 1322 人。這一千多人是否 Random Sample？其餘六千人的數據為何？官方沒有任何公佈。<br />\n<br />\n正如我們多次強調，沒有公開所有數據，沒有經過 Peer Review 的所謂測試結果，沒有任何報導的價值。<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/25/health/turkey-brazil-sinovac-coronavirus-vaccine.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F12%2F25%2Fhealth%2Fturkey-brazil-sinovac-coronavirus-vaccine.html&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUiLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=bce6ffe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/25/health/turkey-brazil-sinovac-coronavirus-vaccine.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3JGbzb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3JGbzb.jpg&h=314df177&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d8b1a2e947de6f43eb03df1207614f88bd1118c","tid":2341690,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾唔夠錢喎"},{"pid":"310bcf49e3fc069b48980325baf00690c5faa734","tid":2341690,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:58:38.000Z","msg":"根本咁嘅sample size就無討論價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae147665f563d5b79d88aed6ffa440ffe0ec149","tid":2341690,"uid":254383,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:00:37.000Z","msg":"你話一開頭就係呢千三個sample 就話唧<br />\n<br />\n屌你原來係成七千個，唔使講都知點解唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad0dd90d063fa249b9424e1a3deb9f3085ba73d","tid":2341690,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>聖誕快樂</strong>"},{"pid":"57cf274d17b7c8834c904b14cf1d28e1532fd699","tid":2341690,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:11:35.000Z","msg":"死咗果啲計唔計？"},{"pid":"d350cc2e3dae80d62ea8982d9814f76d56931456","tid":2341690,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d8b1a2e947de6f43eb03df1207614f88bd1118c","tid":2341690,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾唔夠錢喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"安排多幾次淚曬雪廠街比政客就攪掂啦<br />\n叫埋世衛將變種版本命名為2020英國病毒都仲得呀"},{"pid":"d7b24ce7ee6812867cdbb1d697ba395602337b92","tid":2341690,"uid":100581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:17:47.000Z","msg":"CCTVB： 土耳其剛公布科興疫苗有效率為91.25%"},{"pid":"71a71d9a43c7466fd065c35814991a6a81d82dac","tid":2341690,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7b24ce7ee6812867cdbb1d697ba395602337b92","tid":2341690,"uid":100581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:17:47.000Z","msg":"CCTVB： 土耳其剛公布科興疫苗有效率為91.25%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:18:10.000Z","msg":"一定係咁報"},{"pid":"3f8066acb1b4845c82b7ee486c0caefabc680d30","tid":2341690,"uid":116683,"like":0,